{"tid":960199,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾馬利自爆當年險簽沙拿","createTime":"2018-12-29T08:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T09:29:16.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3c13e8c6fd6d25191f64e581700783c9d18e6f","tid":960199,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"Unai Emery has ranked Mohamed Salah among the top five players in the world and revealed he considered signing the Liverpool forward during his time in charge of Paris Saint-Germain but decided against doing so because he felt the Egyptian could not handle the pressure of playing for a big club.<br />\n<br />\nThe Arsenal manager takes his team to Anfield on Saturday for what looks set to be their toughest test of the season so far. Liverpool sit top having won their past eight games as they seek a first league title since 1990. They also remain unbeaten, still with a chance of becoming English football&rsquo;s latest invincibles, following the Arsenal team who were champions under Ars&egrave;ne Wenger 14 years ago. Emery is among those who believe they are capable of those feats and is in no doubt which of J&uuml;rgen Klopp&rsquo;s men has impressed him most, a player the Spaniard had his eye on long before arriving in England.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We spoke about the possibility to sign Salah to Paris Saint-Germain when he was playing at Roma,&rdquo; Emery said. &ldquo;We had some doubts, and then he signed for Liverpool [in June 2017] and these doubts he has broken. Now if you are speaking about the five top players in the world, one is Salah. Today I can say to you, if we sign him, we sign one player in the top five in the world.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAsked what those doubts were, Emery, who was at PSG for two years before succeeding Wenger at Arsenal last May, replied: &ldquo;How he can take the performance in one big team. For example like PSG.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4f7fc57092d99cbc91291a40d0e3c08f556764a9","tid":960199,"uid":11254,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"阿狗傳統"},{"pid":"d0204e48c0e8124b61ac30079a117b30858582b9","tid":960199,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=fItlN44NZXBL7lJw5Qix1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=362054de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周六阿仙奴作客大戰利物浦，穆罕默德沙拿肯定是兵工廠的心腹大患，客軍主帥艾美利不諱言執教巴黎聖日耳門時，錯過簽入沙拿。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴領隊艾美利承認早於穆罕默德沙拿（Mohamed Salah）效力羅馬時，已察覺到對方的潛力並考慮羅致，但最終並沒出手：「當他效力羅馬時，我與PSG談過簽入他的可能性，我們有些懷疑。」 他道出當時所存在的疑慮：「當時我們懷疑甚麼？是他如何在一支大球隊，像在巴黎的PSG有好表現。之後利物浦簽入他，而這些疑團在利物浦盡除。」去季沙拿以3690萬鎊從羅馬加盟紅軍，整季英超以狂風掃落葉姿態射入32球，並囊括多個個人獎項。 艾美利言談間似乎也大嘆走寶，如今對埃及人推崇不已：「現在，如果你在談論世界上5大頂級前鋒，沙拿是其中之一。」 利物浦VS阿仙奴 Now621台30/12 01:30直播"},{"pid":"8d8ab07063c4696cce334a0173f8b82acc44fe0e","tid":960199,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"老實講PSG有冇沙拿分別唔大"},{"pid":"277d9695e1ae1731e9502fd462d915bf11416f54","tid":960199,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8ab07063c4696cce334a0173f8b82acc44fe0e","tid":960199,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"老實講PSG有冇沙拿分別唔大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"PSG儲翼換印花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e56df1e87afc906422c2413b5cabe91e9ac49cc","tid":960199,"uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"277d9695e1ae1731e9502fd462d915bf11416f54","tid":960199,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8ab07063c4696cce334a0173f8b82acc44fe0e","tid":960199,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"老實講PSG有冇沙拿分別唔大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"PSG儲翼換印花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji